{"tid":1538821,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"如果撤回，最開心嘅可能係劉鑾雄","createTime":"2019-09-04T07:57:48.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-04T08:18:55.000Z","uid":301350,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"b05ef5684f0a2344d3adb6c93a637106537a6415","tid":1538821,"uid":301350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:57:48.000Z","msg":"當時佢提司法覆核，<br />\n跟住五月底收回司法覆核申請。<br />\n如果冇收回司法覆核申請，<br />\n你估呢三個月會點發展？<br />\n<br />\n唉，命也。"},{"pid":"db1834cd98c9dee36655a0c4ed88516ab31a8b21","tid":1538821,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b05ef5684f0a2344d3adb6c93a637106537a6415","tid":1538821,"uid":301350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T07:57:48.000Z","msg":"當時佢提司法覆核，<br />\n跟住五月底收回司法覆核申請。<br />\n如果冇收回司法覆核申請，<br />\n你估呢三個月會點發展？<br />\n<br />\n唉，命也。"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:01:05.000Z","msg":"無用 , 賀一成講左澳門會推港澳引渡法 , 佢到時一樣要走"},{"pid":"2afa50b41c998f4d3bd3b2d03841c2ebb1c0eda0","tid":1538821,"uid":293698,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:01:40.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"28b39f04dce8a2addb5ecc84f1cf3b5d926d780c","tid":1538821,"uid":25468,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:05:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">賀一誠參選澳門特首 稱或考慮與港銜接引渡罪犯事宜</span><br />\n<br />\n澳門第五屆行政長官選舉將於今年8月舉行，被視為大熱的澳門立法會主席賀一誠宣布參選，角逐澳門特首寶座。<br />\n<br />\n被問到當選後會否與香港政府商討長期引渡協議，及香港近期《逃犯條例》爭議，賀一誠形容這是一個「好大嘅風波」，指修例是香港的內部事務，他不應作評論，相信香港政府有信心能處理此風波。<br />\n<br />\n他又表示，若他當選特首，會考慮與香港銜接有關移交逃犯的事宜。<br />\n<br />\n2019-06-18<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/341871/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E8%B3%80%E4%B8%80%E8%AA%A0%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96-%E7%A8%B1%E6%88%96%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E8%88%87%E6%B8%AF%E9%8A%9C%E6%8E%A5%E5%BC%95%E6%B8%A1%E7%BD%AA%E7%8A%AF%E4%BA%8B%E5%AE%9C\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%2583%2585%2F341871%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E8%25B3%2580%25E4%25B8%2580%25E8%25AA%25A0%25E5%258F%2583%25E9%2581%25B8%25E6%25BE%25B3%25E9%2596%2580%25E7%2589%25B9%25E9%25A6%2596-%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E6%2588%2596%25E8%2580%2583%25E6%2585%25AE%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E9%258A%259C%25E6%258E%25A5%25E5%25BC%2595%25E6%25B8%25A1%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E7%258A%25AF%25E4%25BA%258B%25E5%25AE%259C&d=s4T%2BQ7CxF5mM3MMXIC%2FEq4leFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=4d7f9bd1\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E6%94%BF%E6%83%85/341871/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E8%B3%80%E4%B8%80%E8%AA%A0%E5%8F%83%E9%81%B8%E6%BE%B3%E9%96%80%E7%89%B9%E9%A6%96-%E7%A8%B1%E6%88%96%E8%80%83%E6%85%AE%E8%88%87%E6%B8%AF%E9%8A%9C%E6%8E%A5%E5%BC%95%E6%B8%A1%E7%BD%AA%E7%8A%AF%E4%BA%8B%E5%AE%9C</a>"},{"pid":"05028314f0b8cce34efb15b257f16e405b5b3607","tid":1538821,"uid":301350,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T08:18:55.000Z","msg":"咁劉鑾雄真係避無可避，<br />\n香港人亦無路可退，一定要抗爭。<br />\n<br />\n兄弟爬山<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}